*
* %Parameters
* comp_select: [1] 1: Union components, 2: PowderN
* material_data_file: []  
* E0: []                  
* dE: []                  
* sample_radius: []       
* sample_height: []       
* pack: []                
* sigma_inc: []           
* sigma_abs: []           
* Vc: []                  
* geometry_interact: []   
* incoherent_fraction: [] 
*
* %End
